msgctxt "84_Young Person"
msgid "The guy parked over there looks like that assassin... I heard that he was on the phone with his client."
msgstr "The guy parked over there looks like that assassin... I heard that he was on the phone with his client."

msgctxt "96_Young Person"
msgid "It's freaky to think that a real killer is just sitting right over there..."
msgstr "It's freaky to think that a real killer is just sitting right over there..."

msgctxt "108_Saejima"
msgid "(He couldn't be that skilled of an assassin if these young kids were able to point him out... But I may be able to get a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default> from him.)"
msgstr "(He couldn't be that skilled of an assassin if these young kids were able to point him out... But I may be able to get a <Color:7>Revelation<Color:Default> from him.)"

